title: Did Biden’s Order To Halt Keystone XL Pipeline ‘Destroy’ 11,000 Jobs?
subtitle: The exact number of jobs eliminated as a result of an executive order to halt the pipeline's construction remained unknown.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: U.S. President Joe Biden's Jan. 20, 2021, executive order to halt construction of the Keystone XL pipeline "destroyed" 11,000 jobs.
